net.sf.jmuserver.gs.muObjects
Class MuStoreableItem

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.jmuserver.gs.muObjects.MuStoreableItem

public class MuStoreableItem
extends java.lang.Object

Class representing any type of item placed in inventories. It is complementary to the MuItemOnGround class, and both include a reference to the item type (stats) and an own set of hex values, given by the MuItemHex class.

Author:
Marcel
See Also:
MuItemStats, MuItemHex, MuItemOnGround
